Package: scientometricsInR
Title: Companion Package for 'Scientometrics in R'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Raban", "Heller", , "raban.heller@outlook.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8006-9742"))
Description: Helper functions and bundled datasets for the book
    'Scientometrics in R: Bibliometrics, Network Science, and Research
    Evaluation'. Provides utilities for fetching OpenAlex data, computing
    bibliometric indicators, building co-authorship networks, and
    detecting emerging topics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE-CODE
URL: https://r-heller.github.io/scientometrics-in-r/,
    https://github.com/r-heller/scientometrics-in-r
BugReports: https://github.com/r-heller/scientometrics-in-r/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    igraph,
    openalexR,
    rlang,
    tibble
Suggests:
    ggraph,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    tidygraph
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
